# Design Rules

- Use modern SaaS aesthetic
- Use large spacing and visual breathing room
- Prefer rounded-2xl instead of rounded-md
- Use subtle shadows only
- Avoid crowded layouts
- Use strong typography hierarchy
- Prefer cards with soft borders
- Use hover transitions
- Avoid plain tables when possible
- Use section separation
- Use max-width containers
- Use empty states
- Use loading skeletons
- Use consistent spacing scale
- Prefer dashboard quality similar to Stripe, Linear, Vercel

Design style references:
- Stripe Dashboard
- Linear
- Vercel
- Notion
- Raycast
- Resend